Package com.spid.android.sdk.listener

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SPiDAuthenticationListener
    Listener interface for a SPiD authentication request, containing callbacks for when the authentication successfully completes or an error occurs
    SPiDCodeListener
    Listener interface for a SPiD code request, containing callbacks for when the code request successfully completes or an error occurs
    SPiDRequestListener
    Listener interface for a SPiD request.
    SPiDTermsListener
    Listener interface for a SPiD terms request, containing callbacks for when the terms has been successfully fetched or an error occurs
    SPiDUserListener
    Listener interface for a SPiD user request, containing callbacks for when the user has been successfully fetched or an error occurs
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EmptyAuthenticationListener
    Class that extends SPiDAuthenticationListener with empty implementations
    EmptyRequestListener
    Class that extends SPiDRequestListener with empty implementations
    SPiDUiThreadAuthenticationListener
    Convenience class that implements SPiDAuthenticationListener and runs the callbacks on the UI thread.
    SPiDUiThreadCodeListener
    Convenience class that implements SPiDCodeListener and runs the callbacks on the UI thread.
    SPiDUiThreadRequestListener
    Convenience class that implements SPiDRequestListener and runs the callbacks on the UI thread.
    SPiDUiThreadTermsListener
    Convenience class that implements SPiDTermsListener and runs the callbacks on the UI thread.
    SPiDUiThreadUserListener
    Convenience class that implements SPiDUserListener and runs the callbacks on the UI thread.
